as discussed in
the preceding overview section, in 2008 the combination of restructuring
actions, exit activities and a loss on sale of businesses, partially offset by
a gain on sale of real estate, decreased operating income by $269 million, or
1.1 percent of net sales. in 2007, the gain on sale of businesses and real
estate, net of environmental liability charges, restructuring and exit
activities, benefited 2007 operating income by $681 million, or 2.8 percent of
net sales. in 2006, the gain on sale of businesses, net of restructuring and other items,
