2006/2007 restructuring actions:
during the fourth quarter of 2006 and the first six months of 2007,
management approved and committed to undertake the following restructuring actions:
pharmaceuticals business actions  employee-related,
asset impairment and other costs pertaining to the companys exit of its
branded pharmaceuticals operations. these costs included severance and benefits
for pharmaceuticals business employees who are not obtaining employment with
the buyers as well as impairment charges associated with certain assets not
transferred to the buyers.
overhead reduction actions  employee-related costs
for severance and benefits, costs associated with actions to reduce the companys
cost structure.
