the
assumed health care trend rates shown above reflect 3ms expected medical and
drug claims experience. the company has developed certain long-term strategies
to help offset trend rates through care management, strategic sourcing
activities and plan design. a one percentage point change in assumed health
cost trend rates would have the following effects:
