and to address
trace amounts of perfluorinated compounds in drinking water sources in the city
of oakdale and lake elmo, minnesota, as well as presence in the soil and
groundwater at the companys manufacturing facilities in decatur, alabama, and
cottage grove, minnesota, and at two former disposal sites in minnesota.
the company cannot
