code of ethics. all of our
employees, including our chief executive officer, chief financial officer and
chief accounting officer and controller, are required to abide by 3ms
long-standing business conduct policies to ensure that our business is
conducted in a consistently legal and ethical manner. 3m has posted the text of
such code of ethics on its website (http://www.3m.com/businessconduct). at the
